p: (3) Sesquiterpene hydrocarbons: cis-α-bergamotene, trans-α-bergamotene, β-bisabolene, β-carophyllene, α- and β-cadinenes, calamenene, α-copaene, α- and β-cubebenes, ar-curcumene, β- and δ-elemene, β-farnesene, α-guaiene, α-humulene, isocaryophyllene, γ-muurolene, α-santalene, α- and β-selinenes, ledene, sesquisabinene and zingiberene.
